Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里既是狂都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是经都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是境都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,境都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴都凶都狂都境都京都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够啦——!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道你们在搞什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是个玩笑 也不是完全没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何意义的孩子有什么用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想期待你那像孩童一般的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常乱来的游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让毗舍丸做她的对手不正是她的心愿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没同意呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不承认这是议会的决定!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要服从「最初之人」和规定 !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是正式的考试哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实是很清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你也是很想见见妈妈的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄狄浦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是要等得花儿都谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这自主行动 才是重逢的关键呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.75,writings4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(193,227)\frz3.394}是姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.75,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}称号 狼吞虎咽全收集\N随身物品 精神 香口胶 糖\N零用钱 两个人3日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:26.75,writings4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(199,255)\frz4.096}出不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该会理解我们吧 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那帮傻瓜都闹疯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 稻荷?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…认为人类的外表也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也不是你们的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也明白你们想见家人的心情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 只此一次 我就奉陪到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行! 别…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固执的臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别碍着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在搞什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一直倍受各位照顾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我觉得对小孩子这么做可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把单方面的期待强加于人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我总是被大人背叛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来彼此都不太走运呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么认真干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就让你丫闭嘴! 你这鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是华丽的兄妹对打…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.34,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(193,247)}为什么搞不坏!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:18:59.97,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz356.178\pos(180,278)}他作弊。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:18:59.97,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(218,248)}用作弊器改角色太卑鄙啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下场挺不错的嘛 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这臭人类!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 真是气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这招如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.57,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(180,247)}上啊 琴!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:14.57,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(176,277)}做掉它!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个事情一直想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一张嘴就是抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却把那些孩子当成宝一样对待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间是没有秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最舍不得的 到底是哪一方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了吗 这精密机器!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家电破灭击!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白——痴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂停! 暂停!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是很可惜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:52.83,writings6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(187,244)}让我们出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.21,writings6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(195,282)}让我们出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:53.58,writings6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(192,245)}出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:53.96,writings6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(200,283)}出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.33,writings6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(212,244)}出去出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:54.62,writings6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz358.594\pos(219,284)}出去出去出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:54.62,writings6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(233,244)}出去出去 出去出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是对他们保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子 你是不是有点失落?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 我都说好疼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是头疼呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管长多大 都还总是打打闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直这么纵容他们 是你的不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能见面了 我好高兴!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也一直都在等待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一旦话说出口 我就会付诸行动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的言语 就是我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看! 是妈妈啦妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾王 吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您之愿即是我之望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回家啦——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变漂亮了呢 小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老了很多呢 鞍马
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还是那么美丽 古都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.71,0:24:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被女人亲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被个女人亲了啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.49,0:24:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能自己一个人睡觉啦 明惠?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.08,0:24:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.80,0:24:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都有了这么多小孩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.98,0:24:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.66,0:24:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.29,0:24:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊 我好像误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.05,0:24:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我重归于好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.86,0:24:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.13,0:24:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能回来真是太好了 古都大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.50,0:24:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一直 在等待着我们的迎接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.48,0:25:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.42,0:25:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.80,0:25:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.68,0:25:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.48,0:25:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也好想回家 所以拜托啦
