Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:24.31,writings7,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(608,0)\pos(283,194)}不保存
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.50,0:25:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴 你已经回不了家了哟
